===Noun===
#A [[durational pattern]] with a duration equivalent to a whole number of [[pulse]]s on an underlying [[metric level]], opposed to a [[rhythmic gesture]].  Rhythmic units are described as [[metric]], [[intrametric]], [[contrametric]], or [[extrametric]].

